Divine Dessert is one of the famous cake shops. They have decided to open an online shopping portal and promote their sales. By automating the process, they can easily enter cake details. They have also decided to offer a maximum of 25% discount to their customers on the cakes ordered, based on the UPI method they choose for payment (PhonePe, Paytm, Google Pay).

As a software developer, your task is to help them automate the above process by writing a simple Java program. The program should store the cake order details, calculate the cake ID and discount based on the UPI selected for payment, and calculate the final bill amount for the order.

